  <mainDescription>&lt;p>&#xD;
    This artifact typically contains the project's structure and methods for the following:&#xD;
&lt;/p>&#xD;
&lt;ul>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        Assess consistency of the baselines.&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        Review configuration management system.&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        Confirm&amp;nbsp;completeness and correctness of configuration management records and configuration items.&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        Confirm if configuration management is compliant with established standards and procedures.&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
&lt;/ul></mainDescription>
  <purpose>&lt;p>&#xD;
    To confirm the required work products are physically present and also verify the documentation of functional&#xD;
    characteristics of a configuration item are according to requirements specified.&#xD;
&lt;/p></purpose>
  <impactOfNotHaving>&lt;p>&#xD;
    Without this artifact:&#xD;
&lt;/p>&#xD;
&lt;ul>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        Audit results cannot be recorded, such as reasons for audit failures.&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        Cannot track the action items from the audit to closure, leading inconsistency&amp;nbsp;and duplication of effort&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        Consistency of requirements as stated in the plan with configuration management system&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
&lt;/ul></impactOfNotHaving>
  <reasonsForNotNeeding>&lt;p>&#xD;
    Some reasons for not needing this artifact:&#xD;
&lt;/p>&#xD;
&lt;ul>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        If it is the responsibility of Quality Assurance team to perform configuration audit&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        For small&amp;nbsp;project configuration audit may not be necessary&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        Informal Configuration Audit may be performed as part of another activity such as release management, security and&#xD;
        compliance&amp;nbsp;and change management&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
&lt;/ul>&lt;br /></reasonsForNotNeeding>
